content: HAPI supports Logical Model? If so on which resource type I can find the message in the UI?

Hi Guys, this question still has not been answered and we (@Alexander Zautke ) have the same question. We are currently trying to parse a logical model but are getting the error message "unknown resource type". Is there any means for providing a custom data type when parsing a resource?

By logical model, do you mean this: http://hapifhir.io/doc_fhirobjects.html
See also the hapi-fhir-structures-xxxx jars in the downloads area: http://hapifhir.io/download.html
